<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<dxl:DXLMessage xmlns:dxl="http://greenplum.com/dxl/2010/12/">
  <dxl:Comment><![CDATA[
    Background -
        For EXISTS/semijoin subqueries, outer table columns that are part of the
        primary key may be required for grouping even if they are not used in the query output.
        Previously, unused but required columns could trigger an assertion failure in
        CTranslatorExprToDXL::MakeDXLTableDescr(). This MDP adds the failing test case.

    Query & Plan:
        SELECT count(a.col1) FROM tabOuter a WHERE a.col66='VAL1' AND EXISTS
            (
                SELECT 1 FROM tabInner b WHERE b.col1='003' AND a.col1::date >= b.col5::date AND a.col1::date <  b.col6::date
            );
                                                                 QUERY PLAN
        ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
         Finalize Aggregate  (cost=0.00..13478098.31 rows=1 width=8)
           ->  Gather Motion 3:1  (slice1; segments: 3)  (cost=0.00..13478098.31 rows=1 width=8)
                 ->  Partial Aggregate  (cost=0.00..13478098.31 rows=1 width=8)
                       ->  HashAggregate  (cost=0.00..13478095.96 rows=56063792 width=4)
                             Group Key: a.col1, a.col2, a.col3
                             Planned Partitions: 128
                             ->  Nested Loop  (cost=0.00..13475551.87 rows=56063792 width=32)
                                   Join Filter: ((a.col1 >= b.col5) AND (a.col1 < b.col6))
                                   ->  Broadcast Motion 3:3  (slice2; segments: 3)  (cost=0.00..6.00 rows=12 width=8)
                                         ->  Index Scan using tabInner_pkey on tabInner b  (cost=0.00..6.00 rows=1 width=8)
                                               Index Cond: ((col1)::text = '003'::text)
                                   ->  Materialize  (cost=0.00..8644.96 rows=280826871 width=32)
                                         ->  Dynamic Seq Scan on tabOuter a  (cost=0.00..7802.48 rows=280826871 width=40)
                                               Number of partitions to scan: 45 (out of 45)
                                               Filter: ((col66)::text = 'VAL1'::text)
         Optimizer: GPORCA
        (16 rows)
  ]]></dxl:Comment>
